
If you have the PyPi distribution, you only need run:

	python setup.py install

If you have the source:

	1. Download libtomcrypt-1.16 from http://libtomcrypt.com/download.html and
	   install into the project root.
	2. Download tomsfastmath-0.10 from http://tfm.libtomcrypt.com/download.html
	   and install into the project root.
	
	If you want to build the module:
	
	3a. Run `make`.
	
	If you want to install the module:
	
	3b. Run `make tomcrypt/_main.c`.
	4. Run `python setup.py install`.